		</filter-class> </filter> <filter-mapping> <filter-name>jsessionid</filter-name> 
		<url-pattern>/*</url-pattern> </filter-mapping> <filter> <filter-name>NewSessionFilter</filter-name> 
		<filter-class>com.exiao.platform.mgr.sys.filter.NewSessionFilter</filter-class> 
		</filter> <filter-mapping> <filter-name>NewSessionFilter</filter-name> <url-pattern>/index</url-pattern> 
		</filter-mapping> -->
